channel.title: Port forwarding GUIDE for Siemens speedstream Routers!
channel.description:
[b][i][u][size=15pt]HOW TO PORTFORWARD!![/size][/u][/i][/b]
------------------------------------------------ Start of session one! ------------------------------------------------- First we need to find your click start control panel Make sure its in clasic view, click on network connections double click LOCAL AREA CONNECTION. See the tabs?
heres an exp See the selected default gateway?
[IMG]http://i10.tinypic.com/4xxckl3.jpg[/img]
Copy or right down the default Gateway you will need this for the next step!!
Now open up internet explorer or Firefox and type in the default gateway in the address bar.
NOTE: IT WILL ASK FOR USERNAME AND PASS!!!
Type for the username as *username* admin *password* admin ------------------------------------------------- End of session one. ------------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------- SESSION 2 -------------------------------------------------
Now you should see something like this
[IMG]http://i16.tinypic.com/6gtub5t.jpg[/img]
THEN
[IMG]http://i12.tinypic.com/6gvz1ir.jpg[/img]
After
[IMG]http://i13.tinypic.com/4u23dk8.jpg[/img]
CLICK APPLY AND ITS DONE :D
------------------------------------------------- END OF SESSION 2 ------------------------------------------------
